{
  "stem": "4226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they just used shovels to put it on, on the fire, mixed with timber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And the, the-- that bath was made-- you went down steps, deep, level with that small river, which was driven the-- which was driving the flour mills.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you had fresh water from that river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was-- diverted part of the river only, enough to, to drive two big--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Beretyo, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-E-R-E-T-Y-O.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a good, good river, full of fish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people even drank from the river who didn't have a well or they had--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the diverted part was fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that, that couldn't freeze from the speed of, of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the main river was frozen over, which it was slow in parts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In certain places where it was fast, it couldn't freeze even that--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--where it was rapids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you could see ice coming down from the big timber, which were-- was catching the water and driving the mill.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It, it was a wheel, maybe four meter in diameter and about one meter wide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the river-- the-- when the frost came and part of it was frozen like candles sticking on the side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it looked like a stalagmite in a-- in a cave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I, I got one, one-- two friends still alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're living in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were with me in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were liberated together, same carriage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want-- I wanted to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The life in a, in bigger city, I like it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never had brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived in Oradea, in my aunt's place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed with her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She never had children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six years, and after the war again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
